			<td><br>Steve came to iSuppli with twenty plus years in the networking and optical communications industry including fifteen years in semiconductors. Prior to joining iSuppli, he served as the Senior Marketing Manager for Agere Systems, where he was responsible for growing the DSL central-office IC businesses.<br><br>  
He previously was the Business and Marketing Manager for the communications segment within Motorola Semiconductor. He was responsible for market development and revenue growth, business and strategic planning, market forecasts, sales analysis and product planning. <br><br>
Steve is responsible for iSuppli’s IPTV and Broadband and Digital Home practices.  
